  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "We release our survey results as a collaborative repository, in the form of a webpage at https://leak-llm.github.io/.",
    "It features a list of datasets, detailing the extend of data leakage for each of them.",
    "We invite other researchers to contribute any additional known leaks to the list.",
    "Work on LLMs data contamination traces back to OpenAI's GPT-3 (Brown et al., 2020; Magar and Schwartz, 2022), one of the first models with APIonly access and limited training data disclosure.",
    "Despite results hinting at the presence of significant data contamination (Raffel et al., 2020; Magar and Schwartz, 2022), the model has been used extensively in research and the issue was rarely taken into account when interpreting its performance."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Work on LLMs data contamination traces back to OpenAI's GPT-3 (Brown et al., 2020; Magar and Schwartz, 2022), one of the first models with APIonly access and limited training data disclosure.",
    "Despite results hinting at the presence of significant data contamination (Raffel et al., 2020; Magar and Schwartz, 2022), the model has been used extensively in research and the issue was rarely taken into account when interpreting its performance."
  ]
